"title": "9512: hell, as an experience",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9512: hell, as an experience",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The state of final separation from God, and so from all light, love, peace, pleasure and fulfilment.</p>\n<h2>Hell is separation from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:8–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:23\">MAT 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:32\">MAT 25:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a></p>\n<h2>The final state of the wicked is one of eternal punishment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:41–25:46</a></strong> <em>“eternal punishment” means the punishment that is part of, and belongs to, the final order of things that follows this present age. This is usually, though not invariably, understood as an unending process of punishment consciously experienced by the wicked.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>Biblical expressions for final punishment</h2>\n<h3>God's wrath</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:22\">DEU 32:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:18\">ZEP 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:7\">MAT 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:15-Rev19:16\">REV 19:15–19:16</a></p>\n<h3>Torment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:23-Luke16:24\">LUK 16:23–16:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:29\">MAT 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h3>Corruption</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:23\">PSA 55:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Destruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:8\">GAL 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:10\">DEU 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:11\">PSA 88:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:12\">JHN 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:22\">ROM 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:18-Phil3:19\">PHP 3:18–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2TH 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:8\">REV 17:8</a></p>\n<h3>Unquenchable fire</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:24\">ISA 66:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:12\">MAT 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8-Matt18:9\">MAT 18:8–18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:27\">HEB 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:20\">REV 19:20</a></p>\n<h3>Intense darkness, emphasising utter isolation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:13\">JUD 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:13\">MAT 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17\">2PE 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">JUD 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:21\">JHN 8:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:22\">JOB 28:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:11\">PRO 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:15\">ISA 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:14\">HOS 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:26\">1CO 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:54-1Cor15:55\">1CO 15:54–15:55</a></p>\n<h3>The second death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:14-Rev20:15\">REV 20:14–20:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a></p>\n<h2>The finality of hell</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:26\">LUK 16:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:26-Heb10:27\">HEB 10:26–10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:11\">REV 16:11</a></p>",
